{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"I published this article"},{"time":2440,"text":"in the New York Times Modern Love column\nin January of this year."},{"time":6840,"text":"\"To Fall in Love With Anyone, Do This.\""},{"time":9200,"text":"And the article\nis about a psychological study"},{"time":11520,"text":"designed to create romantic love\nin the laboratory,"},{"time":14960,"text":"and my own experience\ntrying the study myself"},{"time":17720,"text":"one night last summer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19600,"text":"So the procedure is fairly simple:"},{"time":22360,"text":"two strangers take turns asking each other\n36 increasingly personal questions"},{"time":29240,"text":"and then they stare into each other's eyes"},{"time":32159,"text":"without speaking for four minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35360,"text":"So here are a couple of sample questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38760,"text":"Number 12: If you could wake up tomorrow\nhaving gained any one quality or ability,"},{"time":44040,"text":"what would it be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46240,"text":"Number 28: When did you last cry\nin front of another person?"},{"time":50960,"text":"By yourself?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":52200,"text":"As you can see, they really do\nget more personal as they go along."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56480,"text":"Number 30, I really like this one:"},{"time":58880,"text":"Tell your partner\nwhat you like about them;"},{"time":61760,"text":"be very honest this time,"},{"time":63640,"text":"saying things you might not say\nto someone you just met."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68840,"text":"So when I first came across this study\na few years earlier,"},{"time":73400,"text":"one detail really stuck out to me,"},{"time":75520,"text":"and that was the rumor\nthat two of the participants"},{"time":78600,"text":"had gotten married six months later,"},{"time":81120,"text":"and they'd invited the entire lab\nto the ceremony."},{"time":85320,"text":"So I was of course very skeptical"},{"time":88200,"text":"about this process of just\nmanufacturing romantic love,"},{"time":91880,"text":"but of course I was intrigued."},{"time":94760,"text":"And when I got the chance\nto try this study myself,"},{"time":98200,"text":"with someone I knew\nbut not particularly well,"},{"time":101360,"text":"I wasn't expecting to fall in love."},{"time":104520,"text":"But then we did, and --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109160,"text":"And I thought it made a good story,\nso I sent it to the Modern Love column"},{"time":113560,"text":"a few months later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115400,"text":"Now, this was published in January,"},{"time":119880,"text":"and now it is August,"},{"time":121600,"text":"so I'm guessing that some of you\nare probably wondering,"},{"time":125240,"text":"are we still together?"},{"time":127640,"text":"And the reason I think\nyou might be wondering this"},{"time":130039,"text":"is because I have been asked this question"},{"time":132720,"text":"again and again and again\nfor the past seven months."},{"time":136680,"text":"And this question is really\nwhat I want to talk about today."},{"time":140400,"text":"But let's come back to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":144880,"text":"So the week before the article came out,"},{"time":146880,"text":"I was very nervous."},{"time":149600,"text":"I had been working\non a book about love stories"},{"time":152200,"text":"for the past few years,"},{"time":154040,"text":"so I had gotten used to writing\nabout my own experiences"},{"time":156880,"text":"with romantic love on my blog."},{"time":159920,"text":"But a blog post might get\na couple hundred views at the most,"},{"time":164520,"text":"and those were usually\njust my Facebook friends,"},{"time":167640,"text":"and I figured my article\nin the New York Times"},{"time":170240,"text":"would probably get a few thousand views."},{"time":174080,"text":"And that felt like a lot of attention"},{"time":176880,"text":"on a relatively new relationship."},{"time":180080,"text":"But as it turned out, I had no idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184240,"text":"So the article was published online"},{"time":186160,"text":"on a Friday evening,"},{"time":188240,"text":"and by Saturday, this had happened\nto the traffic on my blog."},{"time":194400,"text":"And by Sunday, both the Today Show\nand Good Morning America had called."},{"time":200720,"text":"Within a month, the article\nwould receive over 8 million views,"},{"time":205280,"text":"and I was, to say the least,"},{"time":207600,"text":"underprepared for this sort of attention."},{"time":211520,"text":"It's one thing to work up\nthe confidence to write honestly"},{"time":214520,"text":"about your experiences with love,"},{"time":216640,"text":"but it is another thing to discover"},{"time":219120,"text":"that your love life\nhas made international news --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":222120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223360,"text":"and to realize\nthat people across the world"},{"time":227200,"text":"are genuinely invested\nin the status of your new relationship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234400,"text":"And when people called or emailed,\nwhich they did every day for weeks,"},{"time":239240,"text":"they always asked the same question first:"},{"time":242600,"text":"are you guys still together?"},{"time":245280,"text":"In fact, as I was preparing this talk,"},{"time":247640,"text":"I did a quick search of my email inbox"},{"time":249920,"text":"for the phrase \"Are you still together?\""},{"time":251880,"text":"and several messages\npopped up immediately."},{"time":254600,"text":"They were from students and journalists"},{"time":257279,"text":"and friendly strangers like this one."},{"time":260320,"text":"I did radio interviews and they asked."},{"time":262800,"text":"I even gave a talk, and one woman\nshouted up to the stage,"},{"time":266760,"text":"\"Hey Mandy, where's your boyfriend?\""},{"time":270120,"text":"And I promptly turned bright red."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273440,"text":"I understand that this\nis part of the deal."},{"time":276280,"text":"If you write about your relationship\nin an international newspaper,"},{"time":279840,"text":"you should expect people\nto feel comfortable asking about it."},{"time":283520,"text":"But I just wasn't prepared\nfor the scope of the response."},{"time":288480,"text":"The 36 questions seem\nto have taken on a life of their own."},{"time":292360,"text":"In fact, the New York Times\npublished a follow-up article"},{"time":295800,"text":"for Valentine's Day,"},{"time":297040,"text":"which featured readers' experiences\nof trying the study themselves,"},{"time":301560,"text":"with varying degrees of success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304960,"text":"So my first impulse\nin the face of all of this attention"},{"time":309200,"text":"was to become very protective\nof my own relationship."},{"time":313920,"text":"I said no to every request\nfor the two of us"},{"time":316960,"text":"to do a media appearance together."},{"time":319320,"text":"I turned down TV interviews,"},{"time":321040,"text":"and I said no to every request\nfor photos of the two us."},{"time":325200,"text":"I think I was afraid that we would become"},{"time":327800,"text":"inadvertent icons\nfor the process of falling in love,"},{"time":331960,"text":"a position I did not at all\nfeel qualified for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336760,"text":"And I get it:"},{"time":339240,"text":"people didn't just want to know\nif the study worked,"},{"time":342040,"text":"they wanted to know if it really worked:"},{"time":345000,"text":"that is, if it was capable\nof producing love that would last,"},{"time":349720,"text":"not just a fling, but real love,\nsustainable love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355120,"text":"But this was a question\nI didn't feel capable of answering."},{"time":359240,"text":"My own relationship\nwas only a few months old,"},{"time":361960,"text":"and I felt like people were asking\nthe wrong question in the first place."},{"time":368040,"text":"What would knowing whether or not\nwe were still together really tell them?"},{"time":372200,"text":"If the answer was no,"},{"time":373880,"text":"would it make the experience\nof doing these 36 questions"},{"time":377880,"text":"any less worthwhile?"},{"time":380800,"text":"Dr. Arthur Aron first wrote\nabout these questions"},{"time":383600,"text":"in this study here in 1997,"},{"time":388000,"text":"and here, the researcher's goal\nwas not to produce romantic love."},{"time":392760,"text":"Instead, they wanted to foster"},{"time":394720,"text":"interpersonal closeness\namong college students,"},{"time":398200,"text":"by using what Aron called"},{"time":400960,"text":"\"sustained, escalating, reciprocal,\npersonalistic self-disclosure.\""},{"time":405880,"text":"Sounds romantic, doesn't it?"},{"time":409600,"text":"But the study did work."},{"time":411280,"text":"The participants\ndid feel closer after doing it,"},{"time":414360,"text":"and several subsequent studies have also\nused Aron's fast friends protocol"},{"time":419680,"text":"as a way to quickly create\ntrust and intimacy between strangers."},{"time":423840,"text":"They've used it between members\nof the police and members of community,"},{"time":427293,"text":"and they've used it between people\nof opposing political ideologies."},{"time":431800,"text":"The original version of the story,"},{"time":433600,"text":"the one that I tried last summer,"},{"time":436120,"text":"that pairs the personal questions\nwith four minutes of eye contact,"},{"time":440360,"text":"was referenced in this article,"},{"time":442480,"text":"but unfortunately it was never published."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446640,"text":"So a few months ago, I was giving a talk"},{"time":449680,"text":"at a small liberal arts college,"},{"time":452000,"text":"and a student came up to me afterwards"},{"time":454720,"text":"and he said, kind of shyly,"},{"time":457360,"text":"\"So, I tried your study,\nand it didn't work.\""},{"time":462400,"text":"He seemed a little mystified by this."},{"time":465680,"text":"\"You mean, you didn't fall in love\nwith the person you did it with?\" I asked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470480,"text":"\"Well...\" He paused."},{"time":472920,"text":"\"I think she just wants to be friends.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":477480,"text":"\"But did you become\nbetter friends?\" I asked."},{"time":481240,"text":"\"Did you feel like you got to really\nknow each other after doing the study?\""},{"time":484920,"text":"He nodded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486240,"text":"\"So, then it worked,\" I said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489200,"text":"I don't think this is the answer\nhe was looking for."},{"time":493440,"text":"In fact, I don't think this is the answer\nthat any of us are looking for"},{"time":497800,"text":"when it comes to love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500080,"text":"I first came across this study"},{"time":501840,"text":"when I was 29"},{"time":503320,"text":"and I was going through\na really difficult breakup."},{"time":506760,"text":"I had been in the relationship\nsince I was 20,"},{"time":509400,"text":"which was basically my entire adult life,"},{"time":512200,"text":"and he was my first real love,"},{"time":514320,"text":"and I had no idea how or if\nI could make a life without him."},{"time":519440,"text":"So I turned to science."},{"time":521840,"text":"I researched everything I could find\nabout the science of romantic love,"},{"time":526440,"text":"and I think I was hoping that it might\nsomehow inoculate me from heartache."},{"time":531560,"text":"I don't know if I realized\nthis at the time --"},{"time":535120,"text":"I thought I was just doing research\nfor this book I was writing --"},{"time":538440,"text":"but it seems really obvious in retrospect."},{"time":541880,"text":"I hoped that if I armed myself\nwith the knowledge of romantic love,"},{"time":546320,"text":"I might never have to feel\nas terrible and lonely as I did then."},{"time":552320,"text":"And all this knowledge\nhas been useful in some ways."},{"time":556640,"text":"I am more patient with love.\nI am more relaxed."},{"time":559960,"text":"I am more confident\nabout asking for what I want."},{"time":563560,"text":"But I can also see myself more clearly,"},{"time":567320,"text":"and I can see that what I want\nis sometimes more"},{"time":571600,"text":"than can reasonably be asked for."},{"time":574680,"text":"What I want from love is a guarantee,"},{"time":578160,"text":"not just that I am loved today"},{"time":580400,"text":"and that I will be loved tomorrow,"},{"time":582840,"text":"but that I will continue to be loved\nby the person I love indefinitely."},{"time":589240,"text":"Maybe it's this possibility of a guarantee"},{"time":592760,"text":"that people were really asking about"},{"time":594760,"text":"when they wanted to know\nif we were still together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598800,"text":"So the story that the media told\nabout the 36 questions"},{"time":602760,"text":"was that there might be\na shortcut to falling in love."},{"time":606080,"text":"There might be a way to somehow\nmitigate some of the risk involved,"},{"time":609840,"text":"and this is a very appealing story,"},{"time":612480,"text":"because falling in love feels amazing,"},{"time":615680,"text":"but it's also terrifying."},{"time":618440,"text":"The moment you admit to loving someone,"},{"time":621040,"text":"you admit to having a lot to lose,"},{"time":624640,"text":"and it's true that these questions\ndo provide a mechanism"},{"time":628880,"text":"for getting to know someone quickly,"},{"time":631200,"text":"which is also a mechanism for being known,"},{"time":633760,"text":"and I think this is the thing\nthat most of us really want from love:"},{"time":638240,"text":"to be known, to be seen, to be understood."},{"time":643200,"text":"But I think when it comes to love,"},{"time":645160,"text":"we are too willing to accept\nthe short version of the story."},{"time":649680,"text":"The version of the story that asks,\n\"Are you still together?\""},{"time":653280,"text":"and is content with a yes or no answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657560,"text":"So rather than that question,"},{"time":659520,"text":"I would propose we ask\nsome more difficult questions,"},{"time":663200,"text":"questions like:"},{"time":665080,"text":"How do you decide who deserves your love"},{"time":668120,"text":"and who does not?"},{"time":670840,"text":"How do you stay in love\nwhen things get difficult,"},{"time":674120,"text":"and how do you know\nwhen to just cut and run?"},{"time":677880,"text":"How do you live with the doubt"},{"time":679800,"text":"that inevitably creeps\ninto every relationship,"},{"time":682840,"text":"or even harder,"},{"time":684480,"text":"how do you live with your partner's doubt?"},{"time":687800,"text":"I don't necessarily know\nthe answers to these questions,"},{"time":691440,"text":"but I think they're an important start\nat having a more thoughtful conversation"},{"time":696600,"text":"about what it means to love someone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":700080,"text":"So, if you want it,"},{"time":702440,"text":"the short version of the story\nof my relationship is this:"},{"time":706760,"text":"a year ago, an acquaintance\nand I did a study"},{"time":709880,"text":"designed to create romantic love,"},{"time":712600,"text":"and we fell in love,"},{"time":714320,"text":"and we are still together,"},{"time":716200,"text":"and I am so glad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719040,"text":"But falling in love is not\nthe same thing as staying in love."},{"time":724440,"text":"Falling in love is the easy part."},{"time":728360,"text":"So at the end of my article, I wrote,\n\"Love didn't happen to us."},{"time":732760,"text":"We're in love because we each\nmade the choice to be.\""},{"time":736080,"text":"And I cringe a little\nwhen I read that now,"},{"time":740280,"text":"not because it isn't true,"},{"time":742600,"text":"but because at the time,\nI really hadn't considered"},{"time":745840,"text":"everything that was contained\nin that choice."},{"time":749480,"text":"I didn't consider how many times\nwe would each have to make that choice,"},{"time":754720,"text":"and how many times I will continue\nto have to make that choice"},{"time":758320,"text":"without knowing whether or not\nhe will always choose me."},{"time":762160,"text":"I want it to be enough to have asked\nand answered 36 questions,"},{"time":767680,"text":"and to have chosen to love someone\nso generous and kind and fun"},{"time":772920,"text":"and to have broadcast that choice\nin the biggest newspaper in America."},{"time":778880,"text":"But what I have done instead\nis turn my relationship"},{"time":782000,"text":"into the kind of myth\nI don't quite believe in."},{"time":786200,"text":"And what I want, what perhaps\nI will spend my life wanting,"},{"time":790480,"text":"is for that myth to be true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":793200,"text":"I want the happy ending\nimplied by the title to my article,"},{"time":798000,"text":"which is, incidentally,"},{"time":799520,"text":"the only part of the article\nthat I didn't actually write."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":806520,"text":"But what I have instead is the chance\nto make the choice to love someone,"},{"time":811240,"text":"and the hope that he will choose\nto love me back,"},{"time":814720,"text":"and it is terrifying,"},{"time":817440,"text":"but that's the deal with love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":819200,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}